{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_SetMass}}

'''A_SetMass''' (int ''mass'')

Changes the calling actor's mass to ''mass''. It can be used with the ''mass'' [[DECORATE expressions|DECORATE variable]] to modify the actor's current mass.

